entry.title: Sylvanian Families Baby Treat Series Blind Bag - Random Bag x 1
entry.summary:
Vendor: Sylvanian Families
Type: Toys
Price: 9.90

Sylvanian Families Baby Treat Blind Bag - 1 x Random bag - part of the Baby Treat Blind Bag series.

The Baby Treat Series features eight different sealed mystery bags, each containing a baby figure with a specific treat.  The mystery is that you wont know which one you've got until you have opened the pack to reveal who is inside! 

In this sale you will be purchasing 1 x random bag (and you will randomly receive 1 of the figures and their specific accessory listed below)

Please note, that if choosing more than one random bag, there is a possibility you may end up with more than one of the same figure. Bags are sealed and we have no way of knowing which figures you will receive. In the case of double-ups we do not exchange or take returns on these items, as this is part of the fun and chance of the "random" pick.

The possible figures and accessories you MAY find inside (remember, you won't know which one you are receiving as this is a random, sealed bag)

Baby Treats Series Blind Bags - Mystery Packs [Season 8]

Everyone in Sylvania loves surprises, and that’s just what you’ll get from the Baby Treats Series of Blind Bags! These colourful mystery packs each contain a baby figure, and a cute animal-themed sweet treat to match. The mystery is that you won’t know which one you’ve got until you have opened the pack to reveal who is inside!

There are 8 different sets to collect, swap and trade with your friends to complete your entire baby treats series:

  1. Andy Snow Rabbit with rabbit waffle
  2. Bradley Osborne Bear with bear bagel
  3. Scott Sandy Striped Cat with cat muffin
  4. Clara Pookie Panda with panda pancake
  5. Adelaide Outback Koala with koala ice cream
  6. Oscar Buckley Deer with deer lollipop
  7. Albert Marshmallow Mouse with mouse cake
  8. Mystery eight figure to collect!
Each blind bag contains one baby figure and one animal-themed sweet treat.
Contents cannot be specified and there are 8 different figures with accessories to collect.
 
 Bags are chosen at random from a boxful as per the picture below. We just pick one out, with no idea which you will receive. 

 


Price is for one mystery bag containing one random figure.

Ages: 3+

(SF5648)

entry.title: Sylvanian Families Blind Bags Baby Costume Series - Purchase all 8
entry.summary:
Vendor: Sylvanian Families
Type: Toy
Price: 105.00

Sylvanian Families  Baby Costume Series #5
BUY ALL 8 at once!
(Please note that these have been unsealed to check which item and resealed)
 
Now Sylvanian Families have introduced their own series of blind bags!
And we're loving it! 
These are a limited edition set - released this year only.
There are 8 Sylvanian Families babies that come with either their cute costume or an accessory.
*
Perfect to add to your Sylvanian nursery, to add an extra baby to a family that you already have, or just as a cute collectible alone.
*
This set contains 8 baby figures:
1.       Crème Chocolate Rabbit in mermaid costume
2.       Henry Periwinkle Rabbit in prince costume
3.       Angelica Marlow Tuxedo Cat in princess costume
4.       Jenny Brightfield Goat with fairy wand
5.       Alyssa Walnut Squirrel in pirate hat
6.       Matthew Buckley Red Deer in wizard hat
7.       Brianna Persian Cat in ghost costume (a teeny triplet size baby Persian cat)
8.     Mystery baby figure and costume (hint: it's a teeny triplet size baby)


Note that all figures are regular Sylvanian baby size, with the exception of #4 the Persian baby and the Mystery figure which are both small, triplet size baby figures.
Other blind bag series are available too in our 

Sylvanian Families Blind Bag Collection

Being Blind Bags, usually these items are sealed and a mystery. You buy one, but don't know which one you'll end up with. If you wish to do this we have Sylvanian Families Mystery Blind Bags available too.
*
But we've also made it possible to buy all 8 at once.
Please note that these blind bags have been opened to check which band members it contains and resealed. This is because it's impossible to tell which member it contains otherwise.
Or if you are looking for a specific blind bag figure to complete your collection you will find them here -
Sylvanian Families Blind Bags Select your own

Condition: Brand new
Packaging: Unsealed to check contents and resealed with tape.
Age 3+

HAVE FUN COLLECTING THIS ADORABLE SERIES!
